{"tid":917272,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得班 nursing 撚好扮野？","createTime":"2018-11-26T09:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T11:33:34.000Z","uid":68626,"like":30,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"71fe8a220d4c70ae5d1d6b92ced393259c490c2c","tid":917272,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"明明就係貪份高人工 先狗沖去做<br />\n如果同普通文職仔差唔多人工<br />\n仲有冇咁多人狗沖呀<br />\n明明貪錢講到自己好撚偉大咁<br />\n人地唔識d nursing 野就第一時間衝出黎屌人先<br />\n之後係到拋書包<br />\n之後日日呻自己好撚辛苦<br />\n丫你唔明嫁啦xyz<br />\n正常人又點會明呀<br />\n知我唔明你又呻<br />\n屌你老味呀叔我做地盤仲辛苦啦 咪又係日日收工番屋企訓教<br />\n知唔知咩叫人工包埋呀 收得錢就咪撚呻啦<br />\n諗定下面回覆: 係咪人工高唔呻得？/樓主入唔到nursing成浸酸味/慢慢係到酸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e580b88db4154092e88676168b7bd411a792dd23","tid":917272,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"啱呀，啱撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209a3f6861a1cdce9db28563ee40f2f043d0b1ad","tid":917272,"uid":185006,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:10:42.000Z","msg":"其中一個乞人憎既原因係因為做呢行女人多 自然西女人比例都會比較高"},{"pid":"d9509e32767a2d39e641c733cf486bc0d5ef558c","tid":917272,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:15:09.000Z","msg":"西屬性"},{"pid":"6affd3fbeaac0a88fedfb453169925e38c9c2637","tid":917272,"uid":10208,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:15:37.000Z","msg":"為左人工又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地工作內容的確係直接幫到人<br />\n兩者唔可以共存嫁咩，一定要幫到人得黎人工低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"6e2912894931701ec44d2201aae1f6d2a74df3f6","tid":917272,"uid":204358,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"部分同意。我都認為份糧包左。<br />\n利伸:護士"},{"pid":"529c9ada1e9b05ab1fec3561b4a80e6ac04305de","tid":917272,"uid":193192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite